Wayne McCurrie from FNB Wealth & Investments chose Mondi as his stock pick of the day and David Shapiro from Sasfin Securities chose Naspers. McCurrie said: “Mondi is a quality company, it’s proven itself time and time again to actually be a good well-run business.” Shapiro said: “I’m going for Naspers, it’s ahead of the Prosus launch and there’s a chance this thing could work well.” Or listen to the full audio: Subscribe: iono.fm | Apple Podcasts | Pocket Casts | Player.fm